'''Coliseo de Arecibo Manuel G. Iguina Reyes''' (English: ''Manuel Iguina Coliseum'') is an [[indoor arena|indoor sporting arena]] located in [[Arecibo, Puerto Rico|Arecibo]], [[Puerto Rico]].  The capacity of the arena is 12,500 persons. The Coliseo Manuel Iguina is also known as [[Coliseo de Arecibo]].  It is managed by Capitanes de Arecibo Interprise. It is the home of [[Capitanes de Arecibo]] basketball and volleyball team.
The basketball team is a member of [[Baloncesto Superior Nacional]].

