====Iceland's Strongest Man (IFSA)==== The [[International Federation of Strength Athletes|IFSA]] organised the Iceland's Strongest Man competition for a number of years before 2005. However, when the IFSA disassociated from the [[World's Strongest Man]] competition, Iceland's Strongest Man remained the official qualifier with no IFSA involvement. The IFSA did continue to promote their own version until their financial demise at the end of 2008.
